entertainer eddie murphy has bought chers 
fouracre moroccanstyle canyon estate for about 6 million 
the benedict canyon home has six bedrooms 7 bathrooms two 
maids quarters 10 fireplaces a granite kitchen pool spa gym and 
atrium with electronic skylight according to the listing with the 
