downtown was listed for 65 million and reportedly sold for about 
6 million 
a few miles away in holmby hills the home owned by actor burt 
reynolds was relisted with elaine young of alvarez hyland amp young 
reynolds and wife loni anderson have moved to florida and hes 
anxious to sell she said 
the 6 million asking price includes a 15000squarefoot 
threebedroom mediterraneanstyle main house with four bars a 
