force went on the killing spree after he left his girlfriends home 
wednesday in tiber a village in cebu province 360 miles southeast 
of manila 
the military said the violence was triggered by a love 
problem between negro and the woman who was not identified 
after negro left his girlfriends home he began firing his 
semiautomatic rifle at neighbors in the coastal village five people 
were killed and five others injured the report said 
negro then hitched a ride in a jeep to nearby talisay town while 
en route he opened fire on a group of men in lawaan village 
killing two and wounding four the report added 
he surrendered later and was undergoing interrogation the report 
said 
