that one of the companys computers had been entered but she said 
no classified or sensitive information had been handled by the 
computers involved and the problem was fixed within hours of being 
detected 
the military computer network known as milnet is linked through 
seven gateways to another larger computer network arpanet which 
was jammed last month by a rogue program introduced by a cornell 
university graduate student 
